snippet.textDisplay: This was an awful fight, they both should quit.  Chavez should quit for impersonating a fighter and Jacobs needs to fire his trainer for telling him to be like Floyd Mayweather Jr.  I see boxers try to emulate Floyd's defense and they get caught with more punches than they would if they just simply kept their hands up.  Floyd's defense looks fancy and boxers try to adapt his style but it does not work for them.  Jacobs almost got his head taken off quite a few times when he had his hands at his side in the "Floyd position".  Bro, go back in the gym and work on basic defense or your gonna get hurt in the ring.  Lucky Chavez quit, I thought I saw a KO coming before he became unraveled.
